I"<p>Nepal Telecom just launched 4g service for the first time in Nepal today. After the formal innaugration today afternoon, the most latest, and fastest internet is released to public. To actiate 4G in your mobile follow these steps:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Dial <code class="highlighter-rouge">*444#</code> from your phone</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>then after when you get operator feedback, reply the message with <code class="highlighter-rouge">1</code></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>after sometime, you will get SMS notification for confirmation</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>now to use 4G service, keep your mobile network setting to 4G/LTE mode</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>Surf internet at faster speed.</p>

